161e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">possibilities which our feeble faith does </div><div class="t m287 x56 h4 y17a8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not discern. Our minds should be so trained </div><div class="t m333 x56 h4 y1946 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that if necessary we can present the truths </div><div class="t mbc2 x56 h4 y19cc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of His word before the highest earthly </div><div class="t m7bb x56 h4 y1859 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">authorities in such a way as to glorify His </div><div class="t m1d01 x56 h4a y1a62 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">name.&quot;--Ibid., </div><div class="t me59 x81 h4 y1947 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages 333, 334. </div><div class="t m349a x8f h5f yb05 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[901 </div><div class="t mc28 xbc h5f y146 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
